ed="T" n="0757c01"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0757c01"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000008805">金陵延祚寺</placeName><persName key="A010050">法持</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0757c02"/><persName key="A010050">釋法持</persName>，俗姓張氏，<placeName key="PL000000008820">潤州江寧</placeName>人也。儀貌邕肅<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1378"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0757c03"/>膚體至潤，幼而棄俗，長事<ref type="person" target="#A010049">明師</ref>，天機內發，識<lb
ed="T" n="0757c04"/>浪<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1379"/>外澄。<date key="j19573721957736" from-iso="+0647-01-01" to-iso="+0647-12-31">年十三</date><ptr target="#n1360"/>，聞<placeName key="PL000000028124">黃梅</placeName><persName key="A000237">忍<roleName>大師</roleName></persName>，特往<anchor xml:id="beg0757sgsz5"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0757sgsz5"/>謁，<lb
ed="T" n="0757c05"/>蒙示法要，領解幽玄。後歸<placeName key="PL000000009132">青山</placeName>，重事<persName key="A010049">方<roleName>禪<lb
ed="T" n="0757c06"/>師</roleName></persName>，更明宗極<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1380"/>，命其入室<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1381"/>，傳燈繼明，紹迹<lb
ed="T" n="0757c07"/>山門，大宣道化。<persName key="A010049">方</persName>既出山<ptr target="#n1343"/>，凡是學眾，咸悉<lb
ed="T" n="0757c08"/>從其咨稟心要，聲價騰遠，海內聞知。數年之<lb
ed="T" n="0757c09"/>中，四部<ptr type="glossary" target="#g98"/>依慕。時<ref type="person" target="#A000237">黃梅</ref>謝緣去世，謂弟子<persName key="A002095">玄<lb
ed="T" n="0757c10"/>賾</persName>曰：「後傳<ref type="person" target="#A000237">吾</ref>法者可有十人，<placeName key="PL000000008820">金陵</placeName><persName key="A010050">法持</persName>即<lb
ed="T" n="0757c11"/>其一也。」是知兩處禪宗重代相襲。後以<lb
ed="T" n="0757c12"/>法眼付門人<persName key="A010051">智威</persName>。<date key="j19777361977736" when-iso="+0702-10-04">長安二年九月五日</date>，終于<placeName key="PL000000008805">延<lb
ed="T" n="0757c13"/>祚寺</placeName>。遺囑令露骸松下，飼諸禽獸，令得<lb
ed="T" n="0757c14"/>飲食血肉者發菩提心。其日空中有神旛<lb
ed="T" n="0757c15"/>數首從西而來，遶山數轉。眾人咸見。先居<lb
ed="T" n="0757c16"/><placeName key="PL000000009134">幽棲</placeName>故院，竹林變白。報齡六十有八矣。</p>
